  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "\n<p><b>Type:</b> Ninjutsu (Suiton)</p>\n<p><b>Rank:</b> 8</p>\n<p><b>Chakra Cost:</b> 7</p>\n\n<p><b>Learn DC:</b> 23 | <b>Successes:</b> 4</p>\n<p><b>Perform:</b> 11 | <b>Perform DC:</b> 25</p>\n\n<p><b>Components:</b> F, H</p>\n\n<hr>\n\n<p>This technique creates a sphere of water 1 ft in diameter per level, centered on the target. If the sphere is not big enough to completely engulf the target, it automati- cally fails. In addition, the target must be at least halfway submerged in water. If hit, the target is engulfed, becomes unable to take any action and will start drowning. The target can see outside the sphere, but it takes a -4 penalty to Spot and Listen checks. When freed, it will be @Condition[flatFooted]{flat-footed} until the start of its next turn.<br><br>If you lose contact with the sphere, the technique ends. The sphere is immune to damage, and objects cannot pass into, out of or through it. Any hand used to maintain the prison cannot be used for anything else.</p>\n\n\n\n",
      "summary": "",
      "instructions": ""
    },
